{
  "stem": "3453.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this I told them in the museum the same, maybe I'll repeat myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were stationed again in a village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kamadanski ?] ward.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For some reason, they select me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I should be in-- like to protect the general.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was quite honorable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- that's what I was assigned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS] We were stationed in that village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in the morning, at night, we got a order that we must go with the general in the second village.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We must go with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't question where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He-- they give us an order.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We have to go with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went with the-- with our general to the next village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the morning, all hell got loose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Germans occupy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Somebody tipped them off the partisans are in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went on our [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They occupied the village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "High in the big hit and not being a soldier, a schooled soldier, I left my bullet belt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, in the morning, I'm coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I'm getting my bullet belt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I'm getting back my bullet-- my bullets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You don't do it during the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I left it behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] While we were retreating, we used to have we call it the intelligentsia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We call it, [NON-ENGLISH], you know, the people who used to come in the first one in a village to scout out it's everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's not Germans are waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And after, we would retreat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They would be the last one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Two of them, or three of them, whatever we could spare.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "See to it that everybody left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Some partisan can fall asleep, can get a stomachache, can something happen to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
